caption.text:
Funny thing about people is that it takes many differences to split them apart, but it only takes one thing in common to unite them. No matter what your race, skin tone or religion is, we all belong to one nation with one purpose in mind: better future for our beloved country.  Instead of letting our mind to think that these differences divide us, why don't we understand, respect and appreciate our diversity to create better harmony for Indonesia? 
Welcoming Soundsekerta 2017: Harmony in Diversity. Let's embrace our diversity. #soundsekerta2017 #harmonyindiversity
